    stem: 'You\'ve trained an XGBoost model for deployment on Vertex AI for online prediction. As you upload your model to Vertex AI Model Registry, you need to configure the explanation method for serving online prediction requests with minimal latency. Additionally, you want to receive alerts when feature attributions of the model significantly change over time. What steps should you take?',
